_data.name: Design
_data.description: Design articles are based on how to go about planning a website and how it should look. I will also look at existing website designs or any trends.

_data.name: Development
_data.description: Development articles will be on Web Development which differs from Web Design because design is how the site should look, but development is implementing that design.

_data.name: Health
_data.description: Health articles will cover physical fitness, nutrition and mental health which is important for all round development.

_data.name: Media
_data.description: Media articles may cover digital media such as photography, videos, social media or digital marketing.

_data.name: Reviews
_data.description: Reviews may cover anything that I have recently tried and feel the need to share like books, or netflix series, or anything else really I find entertaining in life.

_data.name: Technology
_data.description: Technology articles may cover devices or apps and useful software.
